the "one for you,

49:43.690 --> 49:45.233
two for me" thing.

49:45.733 --> 49:47.318
<i>Come on, reach on in there.</i>

49:48.027 --> 49:50.780
Well, I, um...

49:52.448 --> 49:53.616
Sure.

49:54.951 --> 49:55.910
Which pocket?

49:56.077 --> 49:57.412
It's the front right.

50:01.290 --> 50:03.001
Um, I'm not feeling...

50:03.167 --> 50:04.752
Yeah, go deeper.

