to a conversion camp.

53:43.137 --> 53:45.139
His would-be captors
wanted to deny him

53:45.306 --> 53:47.767
of his true nature, and I
stopped that from happening,

53:47.934 --> 53:50.269
so I will not apologize
for that,

53:50.436 --> 53:52.438
<i>and the people
who were trying to change him</i>

53:52.605 --> 53:54.398
<i>were his family,
people who were supposed</i>

53:54.565 --> 53:55.858
<i>to love him
for who he was</i>

53:56.025 --> 53:58.694
unconditionally,
like my family...

53:58.861 --> 54:00.905
has loved me.

54:03.950 --> 54:05.701
And to not love--

54:06.827 --> 54:08.162
that is the true crime.

54:08.955 --> 54:11.207
<i>And at the end of the day,
everything I did,</i>

54:11.415 --> 54:12.583
<i>I did in the hopes</i>

54:12.750 --> 54:13.876
<i>that we would learn
to love each other</i>

54:14.043 --> 54:16.629
the way that Jesus taught
and God intended,

54:16.796 --> 54:20.424
<i>and, more importantly,
the-the way that we all need.</i>

54:20.758 --> 54:22.134
But I understand
there are laws,

54:23.594 --> 54:25.179
<i>and I broke one.</i>

54:25.346 --> 54:27.139
I set fire to a van,
and in doing so,

54:27.306 --> 54:30.184
I turned what I intended
to be a movement of love

54:30.810 --> 54:32.395
into a movement of anger.

54:35.356 --> 54:36.732
<i>Went too far, Geneva.</i>

54:36.899 --> 54:38.859
<i>I was crazy to let it go
as far as I did.</i>

54:40.778 --> 54:42.905
Truth is, I am bipolar,

54:43.114 --> 54:44.365
I was off my medication,

54:44.532 --> 54:46.033
and I was in a manic state
in which I was not

54:46.200 --> 54:48.411
